title: 이달의소녀탐구 #74 (LOONA TV #74)
summary:
The girls are in another restaurant and they start playing word-chain.
0:13 -- YeoJin loses (she has limited vocabulary) and has to convince the director for
something until he says “what is wrong with you?”
0:34 -- YeoJin: “The director~~ please~~~”. The director: “What’s wrong with you?”
Mission Success.
0:42 -- The girls are enjoying their meal after the game is done.
